headline: Incyte Announces Phase 1 Results for its TGFβR2×PD-1 Bispecific Antibody in Advanced Colorectal Cancer and KRAS G12D Inhibitor in Advanced Pancreatic Ductal Adenocarcinoma
summary: WILMINGTON, Del., October 19, 2025--Incyte Announces Phase 1 Results for its TGFβR2×PD-1 Bispecific Antibody in Advanced CRC and KRAS G12D Inhibitor in Advanced PDAC
